    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Ferret Frenzy</i> is a free compilation of four minigames with three variants each, originally created for Pirate Software's January 2024 Game Jam.   Access the variants by going to Level Select or in the settings menu, changing the Variant Dropdown, and then clicking Play on the main menu. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Requires a mouse for some minigames.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184590/extras/c9c3906020ad1b719de455e36fde677f.poster.avif?t=1770522736\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184590/extras/c9c3906020ad1b719de455e36fde677f.webm?t=1770522736\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184590/extras/c9c3906020ad1b719de455e36fde677f.mp4?t=1770522736\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Animal Wrangler:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Play as Thor and try to wrangle some ferrets</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Catch as many as possible within the time limit</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184590/extras/0420a6c07cf3efe9606f8a96e2d17176.poster.avif?t=1770522736\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184590/extras/0420a6c07cf3efe9606f8a96e2d17176.webm?t=1770522736\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184590/extras/0420a6c07cf3efe9606f8a96e2d17176.mp4?t=1770522736\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Find Us Ferrets:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Find the ferrets in a simple hidden object minigame</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Variants will spice up the gameplay and make it so you have new rules to win!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184590/extras/19e56449db5406d3e1ffd84aab5b4f28.poster.avif?t=1770522736\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184590/extras/19e56449db5406d3e1ffd84aab5b4f28.webm?t=1770522736\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184590/extras/19e56449db5406d3e1ffd84aab5b4f28.mp4?t=1770522736\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Invasion:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Invade and colonize Earth!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Or would you prefer a different outcome?</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184590/extras/9b4efcf6dc5e345da22e22b82aede9ac.poster.avif?t=1770522736\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184590/extras/9b4efcf6dc5e345da22e22b82aede9ac.webm?t=1770522736\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184590/extras/9b4efcf6dc5e345da22e22b82aede9ac.mp4?t=1770522736\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Jam Toast:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Make breakfast with some jam and butter toast</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Prefer to go your own way?  Go crazy and make your perfect sandwich, or just aim for a high score </p></li></ul>",
